# Deploy Test -- KS Global Estates

## Environment
- Live URL check: NOT POSSIBLE from this environment (Zscaler blocks michaelwegter.com).
  Per environment constraints, verification uses local build only and deployment is fire-and-trust.
- Server used: `python3 -m http.server 4090` from `michaelwegter.com/public/` (serves assets at correct `/demos/ks-global-estates/assets/` paths)
- Demo URL tested locally: `http://localhost:4090/demos/ks-global-estates/`
- No auth on this demo (no credentials in build-report.md or deploy.out)

