## Problems found
None. All features functional.

## Notes
- "Beds 5+" showing 0 cards is correct behavior (compound filter with Under $5M active, no property matches both). Not a bug.
- Leaflet tiles load from CARTO CDN -- work fine locally with internet. CDN dependency documented in deploy.out.
- No auth. Hero flow: load -> filter -> select card -> open detail -> gallery -> inquiry form -> saved view.

## handoff
- **Produced:** `deploy-test.out`, `image-shots.mjs`, `image-shots/` (27 PNGs), 30/30 checks pass
- **Decisions:** Live URL not verifiable (Zscaler); all testing done locally against built output served from `public/` root with Python http.server
- **Next needs:** image-analyzer can run `image-shots.mjs` (same selectors, same flows) against `http://localhost:4090/demos/ks-global-estates/` to view all 27 states; proposal-writer references `https://michaelwegter.com/demos/ks-global-estates/` as live demo URL
- **Risks:** Leaflet tiles require internet (CARTO CDN); Unsplash property images require internet -- both functional in testing. No risks in app logic.
- **No backend:** Frontend-only with mock data. No API calls to verify.

VERDICT: pass
